  <entry>
    <title>java新增语法糖</title>
    <link href="/2023/12/22/java/java%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E7%B3%96/"/>
    <url>/2023/12/22/java/java%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E7%B3%96/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h3><p>本文档主要记录java中出现的一些奇怪的语法糖，奇怪之处在于你可能潜意识中觉得没有这个功能，<br>但实际上他有这个语法。</p><h3 id="text-block（文本块-java15新增）"><a href="#text-block（文本块-java15新增）" class="headerlink" title="text block（文本块 java15新增）"></a>text block（文本块 java15新增）</h3><p>可以用来直接创建换行文本，或者直接插入一段代码</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">greeting</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &lt;div class=&#x27;warning&#x27;&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">        Beware of those who say &quot;hello&quot; to the world!</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文本块会自动去除公共的缩进，上边的字符串实际解析出来为：”&lt;div class&#x3D;’warning’&gt;\n    Beware of those who say “hello” to the world!\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n”<br>注意，刚开始的三个引号之后的换行不会纳入代码块的解析范围，但是最后的三个引号之前的换行会。因此如果不想要最后的换行可以把代码写为：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-type">String</span> <span class="hljs-variable">greeting</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &lt;div class=&#x27;warning&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">        Beware of those who say &quot;hello&quot; to the world!</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &lt;/div&gt;&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Switch语句"><a href="#Switch语句" class="headerlink" title="Switch语句"></a>Switch语句</h3><p>java中也是存在Switch语句的，但是和C++不同的是，java中的Switch语句分为两种，一个是保留了C++的经典语句，用法和场景都和C++一样。另外一个中是表达式的Switch语句。具体代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">// 表达式形式的switch</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span> (a) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;2&#x27;</span> -&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;3&#x27;</span> -&gt; <span class="hljs-number">4</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;5&#x27;</span> -&gt; <span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> -&gt; -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 语句形式的switch</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">switch</span>(a) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;2&#x27;</span> -&gt; &#123;<br>        n = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;3&#x27;</span> -&gt; &#123;<br>        n = <span class="hljs-number">4</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;5&#x27;</span> -&gt; &#123;<br>        n = <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span> -&gt; &#123;<br>        n = -<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意，java中用”-&gt;”符号来连接后续代码块的switch语句和C++中用”:”连接后续代码块存在一定的区别。’-&gt;’连接的代码块制定完毕之后不需要后边加上break语句显示跳出，他不是直通型的(fallthrough)。但是’:’连接的代码块如果不及时加上break，他会在当前分支执行完代码之后，继续执行下一个分支的代码，直到执行完default之后才会结束。</p><h3 id="带标签的break"><a href="#带标签的break" class="headerlink" title="带标签的break"></a>带标签的break</h3><p>java中保留了C++中的goto语句，引入了带标签的break，为了方便循环嵌套的情况下，直接跳出所有的循环。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Test</span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">100</span>, m = <span class="hljs-number">100</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, j = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        flag_data:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> ( i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> ( j = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; j &lt; m; j++) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (i + j == <span class="hljs-number">50</span>)&#123;<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span> flag_data;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        System.out.printf(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d, %d&quot;</span>, i, j);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 输出 0 50</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>add： break的好朋友continue也同样有类似的功能，不过break是跳出标记的代码块，continue是跳转到标记的代码块之首。</p><h3 id="后续看到会继续新增-2023-12-22记录"><a href="#后续看到会继续新增-2023-12-22记录" class="headerlink" title="后续看到会继续新增 2023-12-22记录"></a>后续看到会继续新增 2023-12-22记录</h3>]]></content>
    
    
