    <title>0004有序列表中的中位数</title>
    <link href="/2023/12/12/leetcode/0004/"/>
    <url>/2023/12/12/leetcode/0004/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="原题目链接寻找两个正序数组的中位数"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#原题目链接寻找两个正序数组的中位数"></a> 原题目链接：<a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/median-of-two-sorted-arrays/">寻找两个正序数组的中位数</a></h3><h3 id="1-暴力解法-omn"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-暴力解法-omn"></a> 1. 暴力解法 O(m+n)</h3><p>求两个有序列表的中位数，最暴力的解法就是将两个有序列表合并，根据列表长度即可得到中位数下标，根据奇偶长度求得中位数即可。<br />这一步看起来简单，却也是归并排序中的重要步骤，只要了解归并排序，实现起来并不难，注意题目中可能存在空列表，在开始时进行特判即可。</p><figure class="highlight glsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs glsl">class Solution &#123;<br>    public <span class="hljs-type">double</span> findMedianSortedArrays(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums1, <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums2) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, j = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> len = nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span> + nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> []nums = new <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[len];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (len == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> flag = len % <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">double</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;    <span class="hljs-comment">// 计数</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 是否有一个为空的特判</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (i == nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (j &lt; nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                nums[cnt++] = nums2[j++];<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (j == nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (i &lt; nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                nums[cnt++] = nums1[i++];<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 归并排序经典操作</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (i &lt; nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span> &amp;&amp; j &lt; nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums1[i] &lt;= nums2[j]) &#123;<br>                nums[cnt++] = nums1[i++];<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (i == nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (j &lt; nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                        nums[cnt++] = nums2[j++];<br>                    &#125;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                nums[cnt++] = nums2[j++];<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (j == nums2.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (i &lt; nums1.<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>) &#123;<br>                        nums[cnt++] = nums1[i++];<br>                    &#125;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 根据奇偶数得到中位数的下标</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (flag==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>) res = nums[(len<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> res = (nums[len/<span class="hljs-number">2</span><span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + nums[len/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>])*<span class="hljs-number">1.0</span> / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复杂度分析：  时间复杂度O(n+m),空间复杂度O(n+m)</p>]]></content>
    
    
